  "description": "Including nine of Junji Ito's best short stories, as selected by the author himself and presented with accompanying notes and commentary.  It also includes one all new, previously unpublished story.\n\n<br><br>1. Used Record (from Ayatsuri no Yashiki)\n<br>2. Shiver (from Namekuji no Shoujo)\n<br>3. Fashion Model (from Souichi no Noroi Nikki)\n<br>4. Hanging Blimp (from Kao Dorobou)\n<br>5. Marionette Madness (from Ayatsuri no Yashiki)\n<br>6. Painter (from Tomie)\n<br>7. The Long Dream (from Tunnel no Tan)\n<br>8. Honored Ancestors (from Kao Dorobou)\n<br>9. Greased (from Voices in the Dark)\n<br>10. Fashion Model: Cursed Frame\n<br><br><i>All chapters except for 4 and 10 have been adapted by Ito Junji Collection.</i>\n<br><br>\n(Source: Viz Media)",
